Item 5. Other Events and Regulation FD Disclosure.
 
On June 4, 2003, Advance Auto Parts, Inc. issued a press release announcing that FS Equity Partners IV, L.P., an investment fund controlled by Freeman Spogli & Co. LLC, sold 2.0 million shares of Advance Auto Parts, Inc. common stock in a transaction completed after the close of business on June 3, 2003. The press release is incorporated herein to this Form 8-K by reference and a copy of the press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1.
 
