        (a)        with respect to any ABR Loan or Eurodollar Loan that is a Tranche A Term Loan or Revolving Loan or with respect to commitment fees in respect of Revolving Commitments payable under Section 2.12(a), as the case may be, the applicable rate per annum set forth below under the caption "ABR Spread", "Eurodollar Spread" or "Commitment Fee Rate", as the case may be, based upon the ratings by S&P and Moody's, respectively, applicable on such date to the Index Debt:
