This Severance, Release and Noncompetition Agreement (Agreement) is entered into as of December 8, 2005 by and among Advance Auto Parts, Inc. (AAP), Advance Stores Company, Incorporated (ASCI) (AAP and ASCI are jointly and severally hereinafter referred to as Advance) and Jeffrey T. Gray (Employee).
