(g)
any interest or title of a lessor under any lease that is limited to the property subject to such lease; and
 
14
 
(h)
unperfected Liens of any vendor on inventory sold by such vendor securing the unpaid purchase price of such inventory, to the extent such Liens are stated to be reserved in such vendors sale documents (and not granted by separate agreement of the Borrower or any Subsidiary);
 
