SECTION 1.02.
  
  For purposes of this Agreement, Loans may be classified and referred to by Type (, a Eurodollar Loan).  Borrowings also may be classified and referred to by Type (, a Eurodollar Borrowing).
Classification of Loans and Borrowings.
