About Advance Auto Parts
 
Headquartered in Roanoke, Va., Advance Auto Parts, a leading automotive aftermarket retailer of parts, accessories, batteries, and maintenance items in the United States, serves both the do-it-yourself and professional installer markets   As of April 19, 2008, the Company operated 3,291 stores in 40 states, Puerto Rico, and the Virgin Islands.  Additional information about the Company, employment opportunities, customer services, and on-line shopping for parts and accessories can be found on the Companys web site at
www.AdvanceAutoParts.com.
