Guarantor with respect thereto. Any review by the Underwriters of the Company or the Subsidiary Guarantors, the transactions contemplated hereby or other matters relating to such transactions will be performed solely for the benefit of the Underwriters and shall not be on behalf of the Company or the Subsidiary Guarantors.
