the Notes on each January 15 and July 15 (each an ""), beginning on July 15, 2012, to the holders of record on the immediately preceding January 1 or July 1 (each a ""), respectively. Interest on the Notes shall accrue from the most recent date to which interest has been paid or, if no interest has been paid, from the date of issuance. Payments of the principal of and interest on the Notes shall be made in Dollars, and the Notes shall be denominated in Dollars.
