The obligations of the Subsidiary Guarantors to the Holders of the Notes and to the Trustee pursuant to this Subsidiary Guarantee and the Indenture are expressly set forth in Article Ten of the Indenture and reference is hereby made to the Indenture for the precise terms and limitations of this Subsidiary Guarantee.
This Subsidiary Guarantee has been executed and issued to the requirements of Section 4.09 of the Indenture. This Subsidiary Guarantee is subject to automatic and unconditional release as set forth in Section 10.05 of the Indenture.
